<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8"/>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1"/>
  <title>Password Reset Request</title>
  <style>
    body, p, h1, h2, a {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }

    body {
      background-color: #eef2f7;
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      color: #333;
      line-height: 1.6;
      padding: 16px;
    }

    .email-wrapper {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      background: #fff;
      border-radius: 8px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
    }

    .email-header {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
      color: #fff;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 32px 24px;
    }

    .email-header img {
      width: 40px;
      height: 40px;
      max-width: 100%;
      height: auto;
    }

    .email-header h1 {
      font-size: 24px;
      margin-top: 16px;
      word-wrap: break-word;
    }

    .email-body {
      padding: 32px 24px;
    }

    .email-body h2 {
      font-size: 20px;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }

    .email-body p {
      margin-bottom: 16px;
      font-size: 16px;
      word-wrap: break-word;
    }

    .email-button {
      display: inline-block;
      background: #5a67d8;
      color: #fff !important;
      text-decoration: none;
      padding: 14px 28px;
      border-radius: 4px;
      font-size: 16px;
      font-weight: 600;
      transition: background 0.2s ease-in-out;
    }

    .email-button:hover {
      background: #434190;
    }

    .footer {
      background: #f7fafc;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 16px 24px;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #777;
    }

    .footer a {
      color: #5a67d8;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    @@media screen and (max-width: 600px) {
      .email-body, .email-header, .footer {
        padding-left: 16px !important;
        padding-right: 16px !important;
      }

      .email-header h1 {
        font-size: 20px !important;
      }

      .email-body h2 {
        font-size: 18px !important;
      }

      .email-button {
        width: 100% !important;
        padding: 16px !important;
        box-sizing: border-box;
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 18px !important;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="email-wrapper">

  <!-- Header -->
  <div class="email-header">
    <img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/minhsangdotcom/Clean-Architecture_The-Template/refs/heads/main/lock-icon.png" alt="Lock Icon" style="width: 95px;">
    <h1>Password Reset Request</h1>
  </div>

  <!-- Body -->
  <div class="email-body">
    <h2>Hello,</h2>
    <p>We received a request to reset your password for your <strong>The App</strong> account. Click the button below to
      reset it. This link will expire in <strong>@Model.Expiry</strong>.</p>
    <p><strong>If you did not request a password reset, you can safely ignore this email.</strong></p>

    <p style="text-align: center; margin: 24px 0;">
      <a href="@Model.ResetLink" class="email-button">Reset Password</a>
    </p>

    <p>If the button above doesnâ€™t work, copy and paste this link into your browser:</p>
    <p><a href="@Model.ResetLink" style="word-break: break-all; color: #5a67d8;">@Model.ResetLink</a></p>
  </div>

  <!-- Footer -->
  <div class="footer">
    <p>Need help? <a href="mailto:minhsang.1mil@gmail.com">minhsang.1mil@gmail.com</a></p>
  </div>

</div>
</body>
</html>
